

     ___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

                                                                        CDR-Stats : REQUIREMENTS
     ___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________



* Add repository on CentOS 5.4 
--------------------------------

	i386:
		rpm -Uvh http://download.fedora.redhat.com/pub/epel/5/i386/epel-release-5-3.noarch.rpm
	x86_64:
		rpm -Uvh http://download.fedora.redhat.com/pub/epel/5/x86_64/epel-release-5-3.noarch.rpm



* Install Git 
---------------

	yum install git



* Install django
------------------

    http://www.djangoproject.com/download/
    
    First, download Django-1.2.1.tar.gz. 
    
    Then,
        tar xzvf Django-1.2.1.tar.gz
        cd Django-1.2.1
        sudo python setup.py install



* django-debug-toolbar
------------------------

	download :
	git clone http://github.com/robhudson/django-debug-toolbar.git
	
	install :
	cd django-debug-toolbar
	python setup.py bdist
	sudo python setup.py install
	sudo rm -rf build/ dist django_debug_toolbar.egg-info/



* django-dilla 
----------------

    inside the cdr-stats directory :
	svn checkout http://django-dilla.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/dilla dilla



* django-extensions
-----------------------

	svn checkout http://django-command-extensions.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ django-command-extensions
	then install,
    sudo python setup.py install
    
    # very useful to generate graph :
    


* python-dateutil
-------------------

    Go to http://labix.org/python-dateutil and install the last package
    
    last package on date :
        http://labix.org/download/python-dateutil/python-dateutil-1.5.tar.gz
        tar -xvzf python-dateutil-1.5.tar.gz ; cd python-dateutil-1.5/    
        sudo python setup.py install


* django-devserver
----------------------

    inside the cdr-stats directory :
    git clone http://github.com/dcramer/django-devserver


* Extra dependencies 
----------------------
    
    this is already included
    
    Jquery
    JqueryUI
    Jquery.dnd
    jquery.contextmenu
    jqdock (http://www.wizzud.com/jqDock/)
    


* EnhanceJS
-------------
    
    this is already included	
    http://code.google.com/p/enhancejs/    




